caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

.
 Now let 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\mathbf{w}}$
\end_inset

 be any vector in 
\begin_inset Formula $W$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\mathbf{w}}\neq\mathbf{w}$
\end_inset

.
 Since 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}-\mathbf{w}$
\end_inset

 is in 
\begin_inset Formula $W^{\perp}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{w}-\hat{\mathbf{w}}$
\end_inset

